Parliament, Monday, 8 October 2018 – The Portfolio Committee on Basic Education will tomorrow, 9 October 2018, receive a briefing from the Department of Basic Education on the examination readiness for 2018. Details are as follows: 
	
	Date: Tuesday, 9 October 2018
	Time: 13:30
	Venue: Committee Room M201, Second Floor, Marks Building
	
	Meanwhile, the Portfolio Committee on Justice and Correctional Services will tomorrow receive an overview briefing on the annual reports by the Minister of Justice and Correctional Services. Details are as follows: 
	
	Date: Tuesday, 9 October 2018
	Time: 12:00
	Venue: Committee Room 2, Ground Floor, 120 Plein Street ISSUED BY THE PARLIAMENTARY COMMUNICATION SERVICES ON BEHALF OF THE CHAIRPERSONS OF THE COMMITTEES For media enquiries or interviews with the Chairpersons, please contact the Committee’s Media Officer: Name: Rajaa Azzakani (Ms)
